data.description: An incredible opportunity awaits in the heart of The Village of Spring Lake with this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style home. Originally designed for multifamily living, this property offers a versatile and spacious environment, making it a unique investment prospect. The single-story ranch design offers easy accessibility and a seamless flow throughout the living spaces. With four bedrooms and two bathrooms, this property ensures convenience and functionality. Enjoy the convenience of being able to walk a couple blocks to the Lake or enjoy the bike path that will bring you through the Tri Cities with easy access to local amenities, shops, and community offerings.
